Use the standard library
This is how to rescale_to_unit of numbers:
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   Remember that lo is item 0 in numbers
   Remember that hi is item 0 in numbers
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      When x is less than lo, then:
         Remember that lo is x
      End when
      When x is more than hi, then:
         Remember that hi is x
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that span is diff of hi and lo
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      Remember that y is quotient of (diff of x and lo) and span
      Add result to y
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know